{"108","0","Reduces damage taken from all sources to half a heart. #This includes self inflicted damage such as Sharp Plug or Razor Blade. #Does not prevent death from things such as the Suicide King card, or HP loss from things like Devil deals. #Does nothing for the Keeper."},
